Please everyone who loves this show, or anyone who is interested in this download, show some support, help us keep this torrent moving!! :D

@Quemerita, seeding should come automatically once you start downloading a torrent, with your torrent software, unless the software already disabled sharing your upload speed.

Otherwise usually with all software, by default you will be seeding to everyone else.

In order to keep seeding once you finish your download, you just keep your downloaded file on the software, without deleting it.

Hope that helps somewhat hahah.
